{"tid":1490784,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"黑警今日做野咁撚快，一定有古怪","createTime":"2019-08-20T08:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-20T08:19:34.000Z","uid":288018,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"81a942f175c3ec9d12dcbcde25888164ab07637f","tid":1490784,"uid":288018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:03:05.000Z","msg":"平時做野，拉人又唔見咁撚快<br />\n一個鐘內 就拉左濫用私刑個兩個黑警，仲拉埋琴晚將軍澳斬人個仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好明顯係想係開例會記招前，搞掂呢兩件事，等啲記者無野問。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">兩個黑警被捕姐，起訴佢地先係重點</span><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">劇本</span></span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">兩個黑警 拉完之後就會話內部調查 。查幾耐？無人知。姐係由排都唔洗起訴。一直拖 ....等有新既新聞出黎 大家記會唔記得呢件事</span><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳斬人呀叔就會告佢蓄意傷害他人身體。有咁小事就當咁小事。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">警黑一家親。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b69d3d406f25d4a6984a64983bdbb4c2d30a6d","tid":1490784,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"替死鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d07a0ba2c117c7baf272f07bd805def5c890a1f","tid":1490784,"uid":149487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:04:45.000Z","msg":"佢唔拉人，而家邊有野講"},{"pid":"93d2ec9d79c30e00e8fc143a50c7e2019bd7aa51","tid":1490784,"uid":48878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"61b69d3d406f25d4a6984a64983bdbb4c2d30a6d","tid":1490784,"uid":15823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:04:38.000Z","msg":"替死鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T08:05:22.000Z","msg":"你岩"},{"pid":"5246db37e121d58882e5d3f8db754832f00f319d","tid":1490784,"uid":255976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T0